---
// src/components/curso/ResultsSection.astro
---

<section class="px-6 lg:px-20 py-20 bg-[#0b0e14]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-center mb-12 animate-fade-in-up">
            Al finalizar la certificación podrás:
        </h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-12 gap-y-6">
            <div
                class="flex gap-3 animate-fade-in-up"
                style="animation-delay: 100ms;"
            >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 font-bold"
                    >check_circle</span
                >
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >Crear y optimizar campañas de ads profesionales.</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex gap-3 animate-fade-in-up"
                style="animation-delay: 200ms;"
            >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 font-bold"
                    >check_circle</span
                >
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >Diseñar contenido visual pro con herramientas IA.</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex gap-3 animate-fade-in-up"
                style="animation-delay: 300ms;"
            >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 font-bold"
                    >check_circle</span
                >
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >Analizar métricas de negocio y proponer mejoras.</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex gap-3 animate-fade-in-up"
                style="animation-delay: 400ms;"
            >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 font-bold"
                    >check_circle</span
                >
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >Construir landing pages que convierten.</span
                >
            </div>
            <div
                class="flex gap-3 animate-fade-in-up"
                style="animation-delay: 500ms;"
            >
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-green-500 font-bold"
                    >check_circle</span
                >
                <span class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                    >Implementar flujos de trabajo eficientes con IA.</span
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
